---
title: Southeast Asian Sweet Chilli Beef Bowl with Creamy Pear Slaw, Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: This saucy and sticky delight uses Southeast Asian spices and plum sauce to coat beef strips for abundant flavours you could only dream of. The pear slaw provides a refreshing crunch, and steamed jasmine rice acts as the perfect vehicle to soak up that sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65f2734c2d32e2180f38fcfa-b16c7f66.jpeg
